            <title>[LU-17658] sanity check when ofd assign a new sequence to osp</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17658</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the case of ofd loses the commit to update sequence range stored in seq_srv,&lt;br/&gt;
